@startuml C6_tags
title C6. 태그 목록/등록/삭제

actor User
actor Admin
participant "app-service" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL\n(Tag)" as PG

== 목록 ==
User -> SVC: GET /api/tags?target=events|meetings
SVC -> PG: SELECT tags WHERE target=...
SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:[...]}

== 등록 (admin) ==
Admin -> SVC: POST /api/tags\n{target, name}
SVC -> SVC: 관리자 권한 확인
alt 권한 없음
  SVC --> Admin: 403 FORBIDDEN
  return
end
SVC -> PG: INSERT tag (target, name)
SVC --> Admin: 201 CREATED {success:true}

== 삭제 (admin) ==
Admin -> SVC: DELETE /api/tags/{id}
SVC -> SVC: 관리자 권한 확인
SVC -> PG: DELETE FROM tag WHERE id=...
SVC --> Admin: 204 NO_CONTENT
@enduml
